<p>Hi <%= @distributor.contact_name %>,</p>

<p>Thanks for signing up for Bucky Box, my name is Will and I'll be guiding you through your setup with Bucky Box</p>

<h2>What does Bucky Box do?</h2>

<p>We've designed Bucky Box to make 4 things easy for you:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Sell food</li>
  <li>Manage customers</li>
  <li>Fulfil orders</li>
  <li>Make payments easy</li>
</ul>

<p>Have a peek at <a href="http://help.buckybox.com/user-manual/bucky-box-overview/">our quick start guide</a> to get a run down of the major parts of Bucky Box:</p>

<br>
<br>

<h2>Here's how to log into your new account</h2>

<h3><center><%= link_to("Log in to your Bucky Box account", new_distributor_session_url) %></center></h3>
<center><p style="margin-top:-10px; color:#333;"><strong>Your account email is: <%= @distributor.email %></strong></p></center>

<br>
<br>

<h2>Set up your Local Food Enterprise in 4 minutes</h2>
<p>Once you've logged in, have a watch of <a href="http://help.buckybox.com/user-manual/setting-up/">this video</a> to setup your organisation into Bucky Box</p>
<a href="http://help.buckybox.com/user-manual/setting-up/"><img src="http://www.buckybox.com/images/email/getting-started-settings.png"></a>

<br>
<br>
<br>


<h2>Schedule a personal tour of the product</h2>

<p>Every local food business is unique, so it's often helpful to speak with one of our team to find the best ways to use Bucky Box for your operation. While you're still setting up, we offer free Skype voice calls with screen sharing to show you through the system and to consult on the best ways to setup.</p>

<h3><center><a href="mailto:support@buckybox.com">Send us and email to schedule in a call</a></center></h3>


<h2>Join the conversation</h2>

<p>To get the inside line with Bucky Box and to chat to others in the Bucky Box user community, join our <a href="https://community.buckybox.com/">online forum</a> and have your say.</p>


<p>Thanks for being a local food hero, and welcome to your new account with Bucky Box.</p>

<p>Regards<br>
-Will</p>
